[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猫猫温情提示：",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为了获得更好的体验，游玩该个人故事前，推荐分析员优先观看《镜中烬火》剧情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "很久很久以前，森林中有一座小小的木屋，外面爬满了翠绿的藤蔓。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "里面，生活着两只总是依偎在一起，暖呼呼的小猫。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一只，是有着灰色毛发，脸蛋酷酷的，但是爪子却很温暖的小灰猫。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "另一只，则是被月亮施与了魔法与灵魂，浑身软乎乎的玩偶猫。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "过去因为没有痛觉，玩偶猫总是一只猫跑去各种危险的地方玩耍。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从高高的房檐跳下，穿过尖尖的碎玻璃……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她不懂得害怕，也因此一直没有伙伴。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "直到，小灰猫的出现改变了一切。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "他总是守着她，当遇到危险时，就会用那只暖烘烘的爪子搂住她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“会受伤的！”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "每到这时，玩偶猫就会眨巴眨巴那对纽扣眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然她不懂得什么叫作“受伤”，但是她的心还是渐渐感受到了温暖。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而在一场席卷木屋的深夜大火中，正是小灰猫毅然背起她，冲破烈焰。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "自此，两只小猫便成了一对相亲相爱的猫猫伴侣。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在小灰猫的陪伴下，玩偶猫渐渐驱散了孤独。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然玩偶猫依旧不知晓疼痛为何物，但在小灰猫的注目下，她也学会了轻轻走路。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "尽管她的皮肤无法感知疼痛，但至少，能清晰地感知到从小灰猫身上传来的暖意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她不想再因为自己的缘故，让小灰猫的那双眼睛里再浮现出任何担忧了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而也正因如此……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在一个月圆的晚上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "玩偶猫悄悄爬上屋顶。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她向着天上那轮圆满的、曾赋予她生命的月亮。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虔诚地许下心愿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“请让我……成为一只真正的猫咪吧。”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“我想要……”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“去真实地感受世界——不仅是那些美好的瞬间……也包括疼痛的滋味……”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唔……脖子后面酸酸的……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "今天先写到这里吧……剩下的，就去梦里写好了喵。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "深夜，窗外寒风肆意，这几日正是耶洛沙最冷的时日。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好在，这座远离疗养院的前哨站内，供暖与供电系统尚未受到之前那场大战的波及。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哈——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "喵喵喵……睡觉前要先刷牙……刷牙前要先喝热牛奶喵……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唔……分析员的热牛奶喵……不对……是分析员给我热好的牛奶……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "猫汐尔一边胡言乱语，一边晕乎乎地将手伸向了手边盖着盖子的保温杯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "扭扭喵……扭扭喵……揉揉喵搓搓喵……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
