        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就这样，伴随着“啵”的一声闷响。靠着莫名的使命感，猫汐尔强撑着困意，顺利地扭开了保温杯的盖子……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唔喵——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在少女娇嫩的舌尖触到牛奶的刹那，她像触电般猛地弹起身。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "猫汐尔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
